ABOUT MAX PAYNE

Max Payne is a man with nothing to lose in the violent, cold urban night. A fugitive undercover cop framed for murder and now hunted by cops and the mob. Max is a man with his back against the wall, fighting a battle he cannot hope to win. Prepare for a new breed of deep action game. Prepare for pain...

Developed by Remedy Entertainment and produced by 3D Realms, Max Payne is a relentless story-driven game about a man on the edge, fighting for his justice while uncovering plot-twists and twisted thugs in the gritty bowels of New York during the century's worst blizzard. Max Payne is an original third-person 3D game based on the MAX-FX engine and uses photo-digitized textures and radiosity lighting, resulting in one of the most realistic looking games ever seen on the PC.

ABOUT GRAND THEFT AUTO IV

Niko Bellic, Johnny Klebitz, and Luis Lopez all have one thing in common, they live in the worst city in America. Liberty City.

Niko is looking to escape his past and make a new life for himself. Johnny, a veteran member of The Lost biker gang, is caught in the middle of a vicious turf war. Luis, part-time hoodlum and full-time assistant to legendary nightclub impresario Tony Prince, is struggling with the competing loyalties of family and friends. Their lives cross paths with devastating consequences as they fight to survive in a city torn apart by violence and corruption.

ABOUT GRAND THEFT AUTO ONLINE

Grand Theft Auto V for PC also includes Grand Theft Auto Online, with support for 30 players and two spectators. Grand Theft Auto Online for PC will include all existing gameplay upgrades and Rockstar-created content released since the launch of Grand Theft Auto Online, including Heists and Adversary modes.

ABOUT GRAND THEFT AUTO V

When a young street hustler, a retired bank robber and a terrifying psychopath find themselves entangled with some of the most frightening and deranged elements of the criminal underworld, the U.S. government and the entertainment industry, they must pull off a series of dangerous heists to survive in a ruthless city in which they can trust nobody, least of all each other.

Grand Theft Auto V for PC offers players the option to explore the award-winning world of Los Santos and Blaine County in resolutions of up to 4k and beyond, as well as the chance to experience the game running at 60 frames per second.

U0aCA5IpaPk.title: Red Dead Redemption 2 Easter Egg #4 - Meteor House & Meteor Shower
U0aCA5IpaPk.description:
Red Dead Redemption 2 Secret Easter Egg - Meteor House, Crater & Meteor Shower

In Roanoke Ridge just west of Brandywine Drop, New Hanover, you can find a massive crater. Go down into the crater to find and inspect a large meteorite that has plummeted to Earth.

There's also a particular cabin located near the crater. If you go inside, you will find a hole in the roof and a smaller meteorite that has apparently killed the entire family. You can inspect the scene and collect the meteorite, which has an interesting property: it decreases the effects of exposure to hot environments by 10%.

If you head to the field directly west of the Meteor House at around 3am, look up and you might get to see a meteor shower in the sky.

In this challenge you have to capture or kill 5 bounties for Maude in order to unlock the exclusive Stone Hatchet from Red Dead Redemption 2. After that, get 25 kills with this weapon to unlock GTA$250,000 and exclusive access to the Stone Hatchet in Red Dead Redemption 2.

Log in to GTA Online in a Public or Invite Only session and wait a few minutes to receive the first text message from Maude.
You will receive $10,000 for every bounty captured, or $5,000 if you kill them.

- Complete all Courier missions in Los Santos, San Fierro and Las Venturas
- Trucking
- Valet
- Quarry missions
- Wang Cars
- Zero's RC Shop

- Vigilante (Level 12)
- Firefighter (Level 12)

- BMX Challenge
- Chiliad Challenge
- NRG-500 Challenge

STADIUM EVENTS
- 8-Track
- Blood Bowl
- Dirt Track
- Kickstart

- Win all races in Los Santos, San Fierro and Las Venturas (Street and Air Races)

SCHOOLS
- Complete all tests at the Driving School, Boat School, Flying School and Bike School

- Collect 100 Tags
- Take 50 Snapshots
- Collect 50 Horseshoes
- Collect 50 Oysters

OTHER OBJECTIVES
- Get all 30 vehicles to the Import/Export crane

apRqCP5RDDE.title: GTA 5 Graphics Comparison - PS4 / Xbox One / PS3 / Xbox 360
apRqCP5RDDE.description:
Grand Theft Auto V - PS4 vs Xbox One vs PS3 vs Xbox 360 Mega Comparison in Full HD (1080p) by GTA Series Videos [No Spoiler]

WATCH THE COMPARISON OF GTA 5 PC: http://youtu.be/Q-chg06T55Q

All in-game footage from PS4, Xbox One and Xbox 360 has been captured with the same device (Elgato Game Capture HD60) with default settings, while for PS3 version we used Blackmagic Intensity Pro due to HDCP encryption. The resolution of Xbox 360 and PS3 versions has been upscaled to 1080p to match the PS4 and Xbox One versions. We also used default game settings and console settings on all platforms.

In our opinion, the graphics are practically the same for both the Xbox One and the PS4. The only difference is that Xbox One has a darker contrast - which is something you can also set on PS4 by enabling the Full RBG Range in the Video Output settings. We tried to do that and we can assure you that the game looks identical on both versions.

We have only noticed that on PS4 there's more foliage and plants in the sea and on land compared to the Xbox One version, while Xbox One has slightly shorter loading times.

===================================

All Bonus and Pre-order DLC for Grand Theft Auto V

===================================

PRE-ORDER BONUS
Players get access to fly the Atomic Blimp by pre-ordering the game.

SPECIAL & COLLECTOR'S EDITION
Included in the Special and Collector's Edition of GTA V you will find:
● Stunt Plane Trials - Only for single player
● Special Ability Boost - The special ability bar will generate 25% faster
● New Clothes - Gray Jacket for Michael, Blue Denim Jacket & Flames Bowling Shirt for Trevor, Feud Mint Hoodie & Ash Hoodie for Franklin
● New Tattoos - Tiki Pinup for Michael, Love to Hate for Trevor, Chamberlain for Franklin
● New Weapons - The .50 Caliber Pistol, Bullpup Shotgun and the Hammer from Ammu-Nation
● New Vehicles and Garages - Only for the Collector's Edition: exclusive garages with the CarbonRS sports bike and the Hotknife
● GTA Online Custom Characters - Only for the Collector's Edition: Niko Bellic from GTA IV, along with both Claude and Misty from GTA III to use as parent options within the character creation system
● GTA Online Exclusive Vehicle - Only for the Collector's Edition: In Grand Theft Auto Online your garage and the high-end Khamelion electric car, are both purchased through in-game websites accessed through your Online character's cell phone.

SOCIAL CLUB BONUS
As member of the Rockstar Games Social Club you can unlock new haircuts for the three protagonists: The Wood hairstyle and Full Beard for Michael, Randal hairstyle and Handlebar beard for Trevor, Blowout hairstyle and Full Van Dyke goatee for Franklin.
You will also unlock the Annis Elegy RH8 sports car in your exclusive garage and you can buy the Assault SMG from the Ammu-Nation stores in single player.

In GTA Online you can access Red Dead Redemption's John Marston as a parent option within the character creation system.

You will also unlock the single-barrel sawed-off shotgun from Ammu-Nation stores in GTA Online.

The Annis Elegy RH8 sports car will be also available in your multiplayer garage.

NjOKTRiBcEw.title: GTA 5 - Epsilon Program [Kifflom! Achievement / Trophy]
NjOKTRiBcEw.description:
Grand Theft Auto V Strangers and Freaks Side-Mission Gold Medal Walkthrough \ Guide Video in HD

GTA V Strangers and Freaks Missions Playlist:
http://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLQ3KzJPBsAHkmIIrAv_sd_UwoA4FhdUCG

===================================

Mission: Epsilon (Full Mission)

Given by: Epsilonists

Character: Michael

0:11 - SEEKING THE TRUTH
Step 1 - Complete the Epsilon Program Identity Evaluation on the in-game website www.EpsilonProgram.com
Step 2 - Find the red truck with a dent on the right fender in Raton Canyon
Step 3 - Make a donation of $500 to Epsilon Program

4:35 - ACCEPTING THE TRUTH
Step 4 - Wait 24 hours and visit the Epsilon Program warehouse
Step 5 - Make a donation of $5,000 to Epsilon Program

7:39 - ASSUMING THE TRUTH
Step 6 - Meet Marnie in Grapeseed
Step 7 - Find and deliver five vehicles: Pegassi Vacca (13:31), Benefactor Surano (15:00), Declasse Tornado (17:00), Enus Super Diamond (15:53) and Dinka Double-T (18:03)
NOTE: You can also buy the Pegassi Vacca, the Benefactor Surano and the Enus Super Diamond from the in-game website "Southern San Andreas Super Autos"

20:16 - CHASING THE TRUTH
Step 8 - Meet Marnie and Jimmy Boston in Grapeseed
Step 9 - Find the 3 "alien artifacts"
Step 10 - Make two donations of $5,000 to Epsilon Program

Gold Medal Objectives:
● Use the Force - Find the alien artifact without the detector

25:25 - BEARING THE TRUTH
Step 11 - Meet Marnie in Downtown Vinewood
Step 12 - Buy and wear the Official Epsilon Robes Set for 10 in-game days (save from Michael's house to advance game time by 6 hours or kill yourself to advance time by 10 hours)

29:44 - DELIVERING THE TRUTH
Step 13 - Meet Tom near Fort Zancudo
Step 14 - Deliver the Velum to the airfield of Sandy Shores

Gold Medal Objectives:
● Touchdown - Land the Velum without damaging it
● Zondar the Bridge - Fly under a bridge along Lago Zancudo

34:51 - EXERCISING THE TRUTH
Step 15 - Meet your brothers-brothers in Sandy Shore
Step 16 - Wander 5 miles through the Grand Senora Desert (practically the yellow are in the map) wearing Epsilon robes. It will take you about 20-30 minutes to complete this task.
NOTE: If you leave the Grand Senora Desert, the miles of the Epsilonism pilgrimage will be reset, and you must wander through the desert all over again.

41:03 - UNKNOWING THE TRUTH
Step 17 - Meet Cris Formage in West Vinewood
Step 18 - Receive your reward as a true Epsilonist or take the money and fuck Kifflom

Gold Medal Objectives:
● Cult Intervention - Kill all epsilon security
● Show me the Money - Steal the epsilon money and escape

KIFFLOM!

===================================

Related Achievements \ Trophies:
● Solid Gold, Baby! - Earn 70 Gold Medals on Missions and Strangers and Freaks.

● The body has been disposed of successfully.

xtrTzOB5YO8.title: GTA San Andreas - Tips & Tricks - Special Vehicles
xtrTzOB5YO8.description:
Grand Theft Auto San Andreas Tips & Tricks Walkthrough Video in High Definition

===================================

Special Vehicles - In GTA San Andreas there are special vehicles found in some missions that result immune to fire, explosions, bullets, etc.

In this guide we will show you some of these vehicles, explaining how to get them.
It is not a complete list but only a selection of the most interesting or useful.

For many of these vehicles we advise using a Towtruck or a Tractor, both can tow another means of transport making it much easier to bring special vehicles inside the garage.
The Tractor is easily found in the contryside, while there is always a Towtruck available in the junkyard north of Mt. Chiliad.

NOTE: After parking your vehicle in the garage, always enter the house and save otherwise the vehicle could disappear from the garage.

List of the vehicles shown in this video:

- 1:16 - Forklift [Bulletproof] (Robbing Uncle Sam)
- 1:53 - Tampa [Bullet, Fire and Damage proof] (Nines and AKs)
- 2:54 - Tahoma [Bulletproof] (House Party)
- 3:47 - Admiral [Bullet, Fire, Explosion and Damage proof] (Los Sepulcros)
- 5:17 - Savannah [Bulletproof] (High Stakes, Low Rider)

YVwl4bHsfSU.description:
Red Dead Redemption: Undead Nightmare Mythical Creatures Walkthrough Video in High Definition

===================================

The Four Horses of the Apocalypse are mythical creatures that act as special mounts to be found and broken by John Marston. Each horse has its own special ability.

PESTILENCE
Location: West Elizabeth
Special ability: Infinite stamina and very high pain threshold

WAR
Location: New Austin
Special ability: Infinite stamina and causes anything it touches to burst into flames 

FAMINE
Location: Nuevo Paraiso
Special ability: Infinite stamina

DEATH
Location: Spawn everywhere occasionally or you can get it by completing the game storyline
Special ability: Infinite stamina and causes zombies' heads to explode on contact

You can get the deeds for the horses (called "Blood pacts") by completing all the "Four Horses of the Apocalypse" Challenges.

Red Dead Redemption: The Man From Blackwater
Created and directed by John Hillcoat (the director of The Proposition and The Road) this short film chronicles a slice-in-time of protagonist John Marston as he tracks down his former fellow outlaw and friend, Bill Williamson. Along the way, Marston encounters many of Red Dead Redemption's eclectic cast of dreamers, misfits and liars.

Using the world of Red Dead Redemption as a virtual film studio and created entirely with in-game assets and technology, John Hillcoat re-imagines Marston's pursuit of justice and salvation.

Directed by: John Hillcoat
Edited by: Barry Alexander Brown
Produced by: Rockstar Games & Rockstar San Diego

Created and directed by John Hillcoat (the director of The Proposition and The Road) this short film chronicles a slice-in-time of protagonist John Marston as he tracks down his former fellow outlaw and friend, Bill Williamson. Along the way, Marston encounters many of Red Dead Redemption's eclectic cast of dreamers, misfits and liars.

Using the world of Red Dead Redemption as a virtual film studio and created entirely with in-game assets and technology, John Hillcoat re-imagines Marston's pursuit of justice and salvation.

Directed by: John Hillcoat
Edited by: Barry Alexander Brown
Produced by: Rockstar Games & Rockstar San Diego
